text: banteabmk yeung ban phdal kompir dl banda anak del yeung ban chreusareusa knongchamnaom khnhom robsa yeung . haey knongchamnaom puokke mean anak del bampean leu khluoneng . haey knongchamnaom puokke mean anak thoun kandal haey knongchamnaom puokke tiet ka mean anak del neamoukh ke knong kar thveu ampeula tam karoanounhnhat robsa a l laoh der . noh ku chea kar braosa bratan da thomtheng
